SETUP CRONTAB:
--------------
# backup work
0 23 * * * rsync -urv --delete --exclude='/lost+found' /media/vi/work/* /media/vi/stuff/work

# alarm
0 6 * * * ~/Templates/alarm/wakeup


FIX HANGING ON COPYING LARGE FILES:
-----------------------------------
ADD THESE LINES:
echo $((16*1024*1024)) > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_background_bytes
echo $((48*1024*1024)) > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_bytes

TO:
sudo vi /etc/rc.local
